вҹҰ Test async list operations with map/filter/fold вҹ§

О»double(x:в„Ө)вҶ’в„Ө=x*2
О»isEven(x:в„Ө)вҶ’рқ”№=x%2=0
О»main()вҶ’в„Ө=processList([1,2,3,4,5])

вҹҰ Chain async operations: map вҶ’ filter вҶ’ fold вҹ§
О»processList(xs:[в„Ө])вҶ’в„Ө=xsвҶҰdoubleвҠіisEvenвҠ•sumвҠ•0

О»sum(acc:в„Ө,x:в„Ө)вҶ’в„Ө=acc+x
